content: 👋 Hello! I'm Choti: A curious learner passionate about digital skills, data, and solving problems step-by-step. Based in Belgium 🇧🇪, I've lived in 9 countries (Thailand, Switzerland, UK, Denmark, Slovenia, Spain, Maldives, Malaysia, Belgium) and adapt quickly, working across cultures. This international experience shapes how I learn and grow. Currently completing BeCode AI/Data Science Bootcamp

🚀 My Learning Journey: I focus on learning by doing — building digital projects, experimenting with data, and improving skills through real-world challenges. I've learned Dutch, became a mom, and stay endlessly curious. I believe in taking things step-by-step and celebrating small wins along the way. Hands-on approach with continuous skill development Open to various data career paths, with particular interest in roles combining technical skills with data systems, analysis, and engineering.

🎯 Key Accomplishments: Winner of Tech4Positive Futures Challenge 2024 at Capgemini Belgium, developing innovative tech solutions to address climate change impacts. Successfully transitioned into tech while managing family life and learning new languages. Completed multiple client projects and real-world applications that demonstrate practical problem-solving skills. 🏆 Award winner with proven track record in tech solutions This achievement demonstrates ability to work across the full data stack - from problem identification to technical implementation to solution delivery.

💻 Technical Skills: Data Science: Python, Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Seaborn, Scikit-learn, machine learning algorithms, data visualization, statistical analysis | Web Development: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Bootstrap, responsive design, API integration, Git/GitHub | Tools: Jupyter Notebooks, VS Code, Figma, Canva Full-stack development with modern deployment practices These versatile technical skills apply across multiple data career paths including Data Engineering, Data Science, ML Engineering, and Backend Development roles.

🌍 International Experience: Having lived in 9 countries across Europe, Asia, and beyond, I bring a global perspective to every project. This experience taught me to adapt quickly, communicate across cultures, and find creative solutions to challenges. I'm comfortable working with diverse teams and understanding different market needs. Available for opportunities in Belgium and remote work This global perspective is valuable across all data-focused roles, bringing cross-cultural collaboration skills and diverse problem-solving approaches.

🛠️ Project Highlights: Multiple web applications built with React and JavaScript, data visualization projects including coral reef monitoring dashboard, client work including professional portfolio websites, and real-world problem solving through technology. I enjoy taking projects from concept to deployment. Focus on practical solutions that make a difference

🌟 Beyond the Code: Travel the world and enjoy local food (bonus points if it's spicy!). Get totally absorbed in novels — fiction is my go-to way to escape reality (and avoid chores). Learn new languages and figure out how tech can help save the planet — because we do care, right? Values curiosity, cultural adaptation, and continuous learning

SQL Assistant: Ask questions in plain English, get AI-generated SQL queries, and see results instantly.

Multi-Path Career Relevance: This project demonstrates skills applicable to multiple data career paths. The technical implementation showcases data pipeline development, machine learning and statistical analysis.

AI Career Agent Chatbot: Intelligent career agent that answers questions about Choti's professional background using AI and vector search.

Multi-Path Career Relevance: This project demonstrates skills applicable to backendDev. The technical implementation showcases data pipeline development, scalable backend systems development.

Technical Stack: Built with Node.js, Express, Google Gemini AI, RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation), Vector Search, Semantic Embeddings, JavaScript, Vercel, GitHub, showing proficiency across the modern data technology ecosystem.

Detailed Description: An AI RAG-powered chatbot that serves as Choti's professional career agent. Built with Node.js, Express, and Google Gemini AI with vector search using semantic embeddings. Features real-time context retrieval from portfolio data, professional career guidance, and conversational AI that accurately represents Choti's background, skills, and experience. Deployed as a serverless API with CORS support for web integration.


Live Demo Available: **Try it now**: Ask me 'What data science experience does Choti have?' or 'Tell me about her international background' to see how the vector search retrieves relevant context and generates personalized responses!
**Live Demo**: You're currently using this system! Ask me anything about Choti's background, skills, or projects to experience the RAG technology firsthand.
